<plot>Fans of 'Mary Tyler Moore' (qv) may be taken aback by her performance in this fact-based drama, in which she plays a character far removed from her bubbly Laura Petrie and Mary Richards personae. She gets deep inside the role of Sante Kimes, whose childhood of abuse and exploitation leaves a legacy of amorality that she passes on to her son Kenny ('Gabriel Olds' (qv)).</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?336512</url></doc>
